N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 651.3 - Annual report on concurrent receipt of public assistance and OASDI
State Regulations

Social services districts shall report annually for the
month of February on the concurrent receipt of PA and OASDI on Annual Report on

Concurrent Receipt of PA and OASDI, form FP-35. This report shall be submitted
to the office on or before the 15th day of March. Notes
